headline: Is Delta Air Lines (DAL) Pricing Reflect Recent Gains And Capacity Headlines Accurately
summary: If you have been wondering whether Delta Air Lines shares are priced attractively right now, this article walks through what the current market price might be implying about the company. With the stock at US$72.22 after returns of 4.2% over 7 days, 7.6% over 30 days, 4.6% year to date, 19.5% over 1 year, 94.9% over 3 years and 84.2% over 5 years, many investors are asking whether the recent performance lines up with the underlying value. headline: Delta, American Airlines Increase Flights To Cushion Delays Caused By Trump's Restrictions On Carribean Operations Following Venezuela Raid
summary: Delta Airlines Inc. (NASDAQ:DAL), American Airlines Group Inc. (NASDAQ:AAL) have added several additional flights as thousands of travelers were left stranded in the Caribbean amid flight restrictions imposed by the President Donald Trump administration after it carried out a raid in Venezuela that led to the capture of President Nicolás Maduro. Students Left Stranded Due To Cancellations Students returning to school were left stranded due to the uncertainty around flights, Business Insider repo
